          "value": "All holy acts require summoning.\nFor those who choose: The prayer leader at the word\nBar'chu (the call to worship) bends\nthe knees and bows from the waist, and at \"Adonai stands straight. Baruch Adonai is the\ncommunal response, whereupon the community repeats the choreography of the first line.",
